00:13:03.280 --> 00:13:06.640
science and building that, we decided that actually we were going to take a different approach to it.

00:13:06.640 --> 00:13:12.880
So now, like real-world data science, it's a living document, essentially. It's built in

00:13:12.880 --> 00:13:19.440
